### ðŸ”¹ Advanced Queries  
11. **INNER JOIN** â€“ Customers with their orders  
12. **LEFT JOIN** â€“ Orders with/without payments  
13. **RIGHT JOIN** â€“ Products including unsold ones  
14. **Multiple JOINs** â€“ Customer + Order + Product details  
15. **Complex Query** â€“ Monthly sales report by customer city & product  

